      "description": "This car is in fair condition. It runs and drives but has some mechanical issues that should be addressed. The exterior shows moderate wear with visible scratches and minor dents. The interior has noticeable wear but is functional. Suitable for basic transportation but not without its shortcomings.",
      "price": 15500.0,
